query:
SELECT 
  p.id as projeto_id,
  p.nome as projeto_nome,
  p.createdAt as projeto_criado
FROM projects p
WHERE p.nome LIKE '%Jeep%'
ORDER BY p.createdAt DESC
LIMIT 1;
